# Backend Architecture Documentation

## Project Overview

This is a secure document management system backend built with NestJS, featuring robust authentication, role-based access control, and comprehensive infrastructure components. The application follows modern security practices with JWT-based authentication, password hashing, and role-based authorization.

### Key Features

- JWT-based authentication system
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- Database encryption and security
- Comprehensive error handling
- API documentation with Swagger
- Health monitoring
- Caching with Redis
- Input validation and sanitization

